   462→## Testing
   464→First, install dependencies and Playwright browsers:
   465→
   466→```bash
   467→pnpm install
   468→pnpm playwright install
   469→```
   470→
   471→Then ensure you've built the library:
   472→
   473→```bash
   474→pnpm build
   475→```
   476→
   477→Then run the tests using your local build against real browser engines:
   478→
   479→```bash
   480→pnpm test
   481→```

